---
title: Cinnamon Apple Crumb Bars Serves 4 | with Shredded Coconut
description: A Thanksgiving dessert classic, but in bar form! Sweet, cinnamon-spiced apples are layered between a toasted oat  base and crumb topping, then baked until they reach golden-brown perfection.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cinnamon-apple-crumb-bars-5a2068a5-f087af3e.jpg
